ieces were more torn than chopped, so they were slightly bruised and uneven.","The fact that you use a knob rather than buttons proved somewhat awkward as well. Although it was doable, it took a bit of getting used to.","This Hamilton Beach model has some good selling points. For one thing, it has a sturdy suction cup on the bottom, located toward the back, that really anchors it to the countertop. In addition, when we tested with liquids, there was virtually no leaking – that wasn’t the case with some of the top-ranked food processors we tested. It is also quite easy to clean by hand, and you can pop the parts into the top rack of your dishwasher."]},"id":"2a58c160-1932-40bf-8153-1fbf0797a129","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"bc14d18d-fb75-465b-b0f2-235b492ab764","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The Hamilton Beach food processor has a strong motor and lots of power, works quickly, and does some food preparation tasks very fast. Our testing showed it is good for kneading and slicing firm vegetables, but our experiences with other foods produced mixed results."]},"id":"bbd5823f-9063-4f7b-b17f-272ea5f81c7d","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_60343","url":"/hamilton-beach-8-cup-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"angie-parkinson","url":"/author/angie-parkinson","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Angie Parkinson","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"4Pu3Dbh8P3CR8CNSJRVPZP","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2014-08-26T21:37:14Z","datePublished":"2014-08-26T21:37:14Z","name":"Hamilton Beach 8-Cup 70740","synopsis":"The Hamilton Beach 8-Cup 70740 food processor packs a powerful punch, whipping through food preparation tasks quickly.","review":{"rating":80,"verdict":"The Hamilton Beach 8-Cup 70740 works great for certain kitchen tasks, including kneading and slicing firm vegetables, but it produces varied results with other foods.","pros":